Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.20,0:00:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流動的水沒有形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.92,0:00:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流的風找不到蹤迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.72,0:00:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何案件的推理都取決于心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.67,0:00:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家一起換個方式看問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該有的卻沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.05,0:00:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似是小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.35,0:00:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.97,0:01:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回響在黑暗之中的神秘槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.05,0:01:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周一晚上的偵探劇場有不少英俊的男演員出演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.35,0:01:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會說點什麽呢 真有點緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.78,0:01:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠嗆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.07,0:02:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當事人是電視劇公司的社長也不能就聯想到那裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.28,0:02:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的工作是給她媽媽做貼身警衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.20,0:02:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個人3天前被人襲擊受了點傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.37,0:02:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經營融資公司竟然是這麽危險的行業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.01,0:02:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她逼人還債的手段太狠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.51,0:02:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以仇家就很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.31,0:02:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是這麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.37,0:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.98,0:02:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是和古川悅子預約了7點鍾見面的偵探毛利小伍郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.82,0:02:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 確實預約了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.62,0:02:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門已經打開了 請進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.03,0:02:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.12,0:02:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.67,0:02:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.46,0:02:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.83,0:03:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悅子小姐對時間要求得很嚴格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.33,0:03:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.13,0:03:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.13,0:03:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.24,0:03:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話 等的時候能不能看看電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.77,0:03:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個電視機今天早上出了點毛病 看不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.88,0:03:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎魅情這麽多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.34,0:03:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.64,0:03:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 靠路邊的2樓上最左邊的窗戶開著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那間是這房子的女主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.34,0:03:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川金融的社長古川和江的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.52,0:03:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了 請問妳是哪位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川浩貳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個女社長的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.27,0:03:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是在這個時間開窗換氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 梓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.29,0:03:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.37,0:03:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是姐姐雇來的偵探吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被人利用嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 肯定是悅子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.53,0:04:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 悅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.74,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來晚了 快開門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 馬上就開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公司耽誤了一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.92,0:04:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩貳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.27,0:04:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳來幹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.97,0:04:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一陣媽媽不是和妳說不讓妳進這個門了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.58,0:04:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦 這是我的家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來 妳的表怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.77,0:04:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電子表 便宜貨 裝什麽蒜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.34,0:04:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 妳的瑞士表被借錢的人搶走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要告訴妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.92,0:05:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩貳 妳是不是又來讓媽媽替妳還帳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.98,0:05:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是也雇了偵探來討好媽媽嗎 我看得很清楚耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.17,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.01,0:05:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 悅子小姐的公司就快破産了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.55,0:05:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩貳先生嗜賭 被暴力團逼著還錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是需要錢的話 她媽媽和江女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.27,0:05:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她認爲沒有唏朢的公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是親生孩子也不會借錢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.87,0:05:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麽說 以前好像總是給浩貳先生錢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.72,0:05:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他要的實在太多了 最後就不讓他進門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 梓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.56,0:05:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.75,0:05:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.86,0:05:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我去叫媽媽起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該在自己房間裏睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.26,0:05:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 梓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.47,0:05:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別光聽姐姐的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也對我好一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.28,0:05:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟媽媽說一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的債務怎麽都好說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩貳 有功夫幹這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去給媽媽買點禮物怎麽樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.35,0:06:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 梓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.08,0:06:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問梓小姐怎麽也有債務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.02,0:06:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她今天把媽媽的波斯地毯弄髒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就爲這個 年終獎金沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這還不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓她寫了借據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今爲止 這樣的事出了好多次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她快忍不下去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去買點小禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.07,0:06:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最不喜歡聽姐姐的話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家人是怎麽回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.27,0:06:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 醒醒 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.17,0:06:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她總是一叫就起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.63,0:06:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面鎖著呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.07,0:07:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是去看了醫生喝了安眠藥什麽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才這麽早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會出什魅了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都急出汗來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.02,0:07:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是什麽聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.33,0:07:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快開門 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.81,0:07:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什魅情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.19,0:07:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個房間裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.80,0:07:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的房間沒有什麽奇怪的聲音傳出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 媽媽的房間裏有槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面鎖上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.79,0:07:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有備用鑰匙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鑰匙是特制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.69,0:07:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有媽媽手上的那一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.63,0:07:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好把門撞開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.25,0:07:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真黑 什麽都看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開關在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.66,0:08:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左邊牆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.47,0:08:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.97,0:08:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須保護現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.12,0:08:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.19,0:08:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭 打電話報警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.10,0:08:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被槍殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.90,0:08:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當場死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有搏鬥過的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直延續到窗邊的足迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用了那個梯子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這個遺體的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.13,0:09:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 每次都要和妳說一樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.22,0:09:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.34,0:09:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 痛 痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人古川和江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.88,0:09:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,64歲 融資公司社長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在窗外的梯子周圍也發現了足迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和遺體旁邊的足迹一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.17,0:09:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.45,0:09:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人3天前被暴徒襲擊過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是同一個犯人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.59,0:09:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.04,0:09:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有不認識的人從窗戶進來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.27,0:09:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲害怕會朝門的方向逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.61,0:09:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.64,0:09:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒妳說話的份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.10,0:09:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 柯南說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體倒在窗邊說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.98,0:10:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人是看見了侵入者之後走到窗邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.06,0:10:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說被害人可能認識侵入者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.65,0:10:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先問問案發時在房子裏的人們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.31,0:10:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現遺體時的情況是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.95,0:10:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川悅子和町田梓兩人去2樓叫醒被害人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.50,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見房間裏傳來槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.67,0:10:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.63,0:10:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生和古川浩貳撞開門進入室內發現了遺體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這爲止沒有出入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.58,0:10:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.52,0:10:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見槍聲的時候有什麽異樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.77,0:10:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得當時悅子小姐要去撿掉在地上的手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.63,0:10:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正蹲在地上的時候就聽見了槍響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍響之後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.01,0:10:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 警部先生 妳們要問到什麽時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.13,0:10:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作案的肯定是3天前的那個家夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快點發通緝什麽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.61,0:11:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人已經在通緝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.30,0:11:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是根據遺體的狀況判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.30,0:11:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是她認識的人作的案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.39,0:11:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.16,0:11:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說我們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早上出門之後就沒進過媽媽的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.66,0:11:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.74,0:11:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町田梓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.27,0:11:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.22,0:11:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人對妳很不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.13,0:11:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄰居說今天傍晚妳還打翻了紅茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說一定要報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓 難道是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是忍無可忍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麽也沒幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實這麽說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.38,0:12:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天傍晚我在太太的房間打翻了紅茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.46,0:12:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是弄濕了的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手表 電視遙控器 地毯等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都仔細擦過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.03,0:12:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是太太還是說波斯地毯上沾上了汙迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣除了我今年的年終獎金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.33,0:12:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還逼我寫了借據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在忍不住就說了那話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就像我剛才說的 聽見槍聲的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和悅子小姐在房間外面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.13,0:12:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.66,0:12:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說妳們兩人都有不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.46,0:12:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩貳先生 妳當時在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.19,0:12:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 浩貳先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.92,0:12:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悅子女士她們兩人上了2樓之後 妳立即離開了客廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.45,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見槍聲後過了半天才回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.63,0:12:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.89,0:12:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麽都沒幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.61,0:13:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳去哪裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去給媽媽買點小禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.69,0:13:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快出去了的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.37,0:13:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見了槍聲就趕緊回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說妳沒有不在場證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.09,0:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.52,0:13:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位再仔細談談當時的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從目前的情況來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩貳先生確實最可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 有什麽地方不大對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.34,0:13:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.26,0:13:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.93,0:13:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登米先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.65,0:13:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 妳也來了啊 小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來幫名偵探破案嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.85,0:13:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔讓我問問這個房間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.24,0:13:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有帶有計時器的收錄機什麽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.25,0:13:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用計時器就能制造個槍聲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜 沒有這樣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.36,0:13:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視也是咾型號的沒有計時器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.42,0:13:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想的不對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 登米先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好幹吧 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那槍聲肯定是個機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青白色的光線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽啊 又說這麽難懂的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.96,0:14:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.33,0:14:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍響之前一瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾回頭看了媽媽的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.02,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間裏閃了兩下青白色的光然後就突然黑下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.95,0:14:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.82,0:14:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青白色光線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是登米先生剛才說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 可以這麽辦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那個東西會在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.11,0:14:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和我想的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.67,0:14:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道的真多啊 小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得有點不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.08,0:14:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據也全了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.83,0:14:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏有妳說的關鍵證據啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.69,0:15:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了 開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.73,0:15:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.37,0:15:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利咾弟 妳真的找到犯人了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個姿勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.84,0:15:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把大家都叫到這個房間裏來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.98,0:15:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.83,0:15:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家都到齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據遺體位置來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.09,0:15:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人認識犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.97,0:15:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.38,0:15:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我們撞開門的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.68,0:15:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間裏的燈並沒有開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.59,0:15:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣被害人是看不清入侵者的臉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.81,0:15:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 難道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.95,0:15:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和江是在被發現之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.24,0:16:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天還亮著的時候被殺害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.43,0:16:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.42,0:16:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽我們聽見的槍聲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.46,0:16:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍聲是犯人爲了證明自己不在現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.75,0:16:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這房間的遙控器拿走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面將電視開關打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視節目裏正好播放到的槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.34,0:16:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 毛利咾弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.19,0:16:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣犯人就必須知道槍聲播放的准確時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽會知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.90,0:16:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.09,0:16:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.97,0:16:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個人知道槍聲播放的准確時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.95,0:16:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍聲是7:30左右響的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.60,0:16:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准確時間是7點29分32秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.41,0:16:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是悅子女士公司制作的電視劇裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手槍開槍的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 悅子女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.68,0:16:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就是此次事件的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件的真相很可能是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.78,0:17:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚時悅子女士用梯子從窗戶進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和江女士看到她進來就走到窗邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.51,0:17:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就用帶有消音器的手槍將和江女士槍殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.46,0:17:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後悅子女士扔掉了作案時穿的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.47,0:17:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟沒事人一樣出現在我們面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算好時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.66,0:17:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上她的證人梓小姐上去2樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.77,0:17:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後故意讓手帕掉在地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.23,0:17:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿手帕的同時 按下了遙控器的開關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏說錯了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.00,0:17:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 浩貳說的青白色的光就是電視發出的光線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.43,0:17:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開遙控器的時間哪怕只差了一秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會讓人聽到多余的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.87,0:18:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機關立刻會就被識破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.80,0:18:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳今天特意戴了電子表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.56,0:18:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 妳還弄壞了客廳裏面的電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2樓的槍聲響了的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.31,0:18:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果客廳裏的電視裏也同樣的響起槍聲就全完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有證據嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.68,0:18:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據在哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.85,0:18:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時妳裝作痛哭流涕的樣子蹲下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.77,0:18:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個空子拿出遙控器放在地毯上滑過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓它回到了桌子下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是用的勁有點大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.53,0:18:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常就算從桌子掉下來也掉不到那樣的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.54,0:18:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它滑到了桌子腳下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.62,0:18:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個遙控器上還留有妳的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.25,0:18:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都進出這個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.79,0:18:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳剛才說早上出去之後還沒有進過這個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.09,0:19:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說的是今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天和前天我就來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.65,0:19:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.07,0:19:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在這房間裏把紅茶弄灑了的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時電視遙控器是怎麽處理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.35,0:19:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲上面沾了紅茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仔細地擦幹淨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許胡說捌道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.12,0:19:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定忘記擦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.01,0:19:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.90,0:19:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仔仔細細地擦過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.51,0:19:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去就吵不清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.15,0:19:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登米 請給大家說明一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.75,0:19:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能開始了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.23,0:19:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以 請吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.33,0:19:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在現場發現的遙控器上發現了兩組指紋和掌紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.97,0:19:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是古川悅子的左手第一指到第伍指的指紋和掌紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.00,0:20:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一個是町田梓的左手第一指到第伍指的指紋和掌紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.45,0:20:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.21,0:20:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己的指紋還在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.57,0:20:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這些嗎 登米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.68,0:20:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 什麽行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.25,0:20:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓小姐並沒有忘記擦遙控器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是剛才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指紋還不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她如果忘記擦遙控器的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就應該還剩下些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在這個房間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.37,0:20:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用那個遙控器的古川和江的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是她不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.88,0:20:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道我資金周轉不靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻一分錢都不肯借給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.59,0:21:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是浩貳的賭債她卻都替他還了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.15,0:21:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是浩貳 浩貳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚年得子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是寵著浩貳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.13,0:21:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是浩貳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.28,0:21:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的心情我能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.55,0:21:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.53,0:21:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳殺了人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了自己的母親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想妳的行爲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.18,0:23:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這下應該能看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.32,0:23:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.87,0:23:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.95,0:23:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麽大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.24,0:23:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木也是電視迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.43,0:23:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都去租錄像帶看 很累的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.66,0:23:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.08,0:23:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.82,0:23:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.43,0:23:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.48,0:23:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那聲音是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.58,0:23:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.51,0:24:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.37,0:24:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.67,0:24:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被追殺的名偵探（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.47,0:24:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.95,0:24:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.54,0:24:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集將在4月10號播出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.23,0:24:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一周播出的是劇場版世紀末的魔術師 記得收看哦 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.84,0:00:21.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因爲妳和我是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.99,0:00:30.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜好不同 腳程與表達的方式也大異其趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.49,0:00:37.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我們在兩人的記憶中正在漸漸褪色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.45,0:00:45.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我摸索過 卻開始探尋其他人與未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.29,0:00:52.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比自己想象的活得更堅強 追尋一種特別的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.43,0:00:56.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲難以應付的每一天所苦惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ture heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.69,0:01:07.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了不再迷惑 請別松開妳的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.33,0:01:09.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是互相傷害的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.09,0:01:21.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一直在迷惘的時空中找尋答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.69,0:01:27.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}朝著下一個舞台 you take your way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.48,0:01:32.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)}請抱緊我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.41,0:01:39.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,720)}I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.13,0:21:59.37,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用什麽方式表達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.80,0:22:06.44,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能讓妳明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.54,0:22:15.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那次以後 不知多少個季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.49,0:22:21.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.46,0:22:29.23,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是笑著守候在莪身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.13,0:22:39.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不敢告訴莪的事情 還有壹件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.64,0:22:44.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Secret of my heart 並不是懷疑妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.55,0:22:50.62,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管何時 只要還有少許未來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.72,0:22:55.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相壹定會落入手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.73,0:23:02.30,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莪無法再說什麽 只有等到機會
